text: Ceroplesis griseotincta is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaire in 1891. It is known from Tanzania and Kenya.BioLib.cz - Ceroplesis griseotincta. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ceroplesis Category:Beetles described in 1891
title: Ceroplesis griseotincta
